<lb n="0518b20"/><l>霑衣大小便</l><l>染衣&CB01856;認衣</l><l>賒衣果無淨</l></lg>
<lb n="0518b21"/><p>第一子攝頌曰</p><lg place="inline"><l>戶<app type="＊" source="0518011"><lem>鐶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">鐸</rdg></app>倚帶網</l><l>取米為眾食</l>
<lb n="0518b22"/><l>寺內作<note n="0518012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">私＝利【元】【明】</note><app n="0518012"><lem>私</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">利</rdg></app>房</l><l>居人應受用</l></lg>
