<lb n="0518c01"/><l>刀石爪鼻物</l><l>支床不問年</l></lg>
<lb n="0518c02"/><p>第六子攝頌曰</p><lg place="inline"><l>羯恥那衣<note n="0518013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB01856;＝損【聖】</note><app n="0518013"><lem>&CB01856;</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">損</rdg></app></l><l>絣線正縫時</l>
<lb n="0518c03"/><l>染汁雜物等</l><l>用時不應奪</l></lg>
