<lb n="0518c21"/><l>香臺五六年</l><l>並應為大會</l></lg>
<lb n="0518c22"/><p>第五子攝頌曰</p><lg place="inline"><l>大會食草稕</l><l>不應雜亂坐</l>
<lb n="0518c23"/><l>應打<note n="0518018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">揵＝健【聖】</note><app n="0518018"><lem>揵</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">健</rdg></app><note n="0518019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">稚＝椎【三】【宮】</note><note n="0518019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">稚＝椎【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0518019"><lem>稚</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">椎</rdg></app>鼓</l><l>告時令普知</l></lg>
