<lb n="0518c26"/><p><note n="0518020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（大門…曰）六字∞（目得…頌）七字【明】</note><note n="0518020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（大門總攝頌曰）六字∞（目得迦四十八頌）七字【明】</note><app n="0518020"><lem>大門總攝頌曰</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">目得迦四十八頌</rdg></app><note n="0518021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（大門…曰）六字∞（目得…頌）七字【明】，〔目得迦四十八頌〕－【宋】【元】【宮】【聖】</note><note n="0518021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（大門總攝頌曰）六字∞（目得迦四十八頌）七字【明】，〔目得迦四十八頌〕－【宋】【元】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="0518021"><lem><note place="inline">目得迦四十八頌</note></lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho"><note place="inline">大門總攝頌曰</note></rdg><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【宮】【聖】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></p><lg place="inline"><l>最初為懺謝</l>
