<lb n="0519b15"/><lg><l>資<note n="0519010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">具＝貝【聖】</note><app n="0519010"><lem>具</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">貝</rdg></app>衣愚癡</l><l>若差不用俗</l>
