<lb n="0519b17"/><l><note n="0519011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">飯＝餅【三】【宮】</note><note n="0519011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">飯＝餅【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0519011"><lem>飯</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">餅</rdg></app>酪葉承水</l><l>及洗&CB00425;等事</l>
